This species was described from Argentina (Buenos Aires). It is currently known from Brazil (Espírito Santo, Rio de Janeiro, São Paulo, Paraná, Santa Catarina, Rio Grande do Sul), Paraguay, Argentina (Catamarca, Salta, Tucumán, Santiago del Estero, Córdoba, Mendoza, San Juan, San Luís, Formosa, Misiones, Chaco, Santa Fé, Corrientes, Entre Ríos, Buenos Aires, La Pampa, Rio Negro, Neuquén), and Uruguay (
